09:51.206 --> 09:54.103
Docket ending 934,
The People versus Fabian Reyes.

09:54.241 --> 09:56.379
- Step up.
- Okay.

09:57.103 --> 09:59.620
- What do we got?
- Return on a warrant, Judge.

09:59.758 --> 10:01.620
Desk appearance ticket,
unlicensed dog,

10:01.758 --> 10:03.034
no vaccination certificate.

10:03.172 --> 10:04.862
