showed up for court.

10:05.000 --> 10:07.068
The People offer
three days' community service.

10:07.206 --> 10:09.000
Your Honor, he's already
been in here almost two days.

10:09.137 --> 10:10.758
Well, when you don't come back
the first time,

10:10.896 --> 10:12.517
you get the slow justice.

10:12.827 --> 10:14.620
His friend said that he would
take care of the ticket.

10:14.758 --> 10:16.758
