10:22.310 --> 10:24.241
Your Honor,
the dog wasn't even his.

10:24.379 --> 10:25.827
He was walking it for a friend.

10:25.965 --> 10:28.655
Post bail or plead guilty.
I got cases to move here.

10:28.793 --> 10:31.000
