a disciplinary tactic

11:06.655 --> 11:08.931
is barbaric
and completely ineffective.

11:09.068 --> 11:11.379
Any individual who engages
in corporal punishment

11:11.517 --> 11:13.137
should be prosecuted
to the full extent

11:13.275 --> 11:14.655
of the law where appropriate."

11:14.793 --> 11:16.793
I'm not recusing myself
because you stumbled

11:16.931 --> 11:19.241
onto some posts
you suspect I wrote.

11:19.379 --> 11:21.655
We're prepared
to subpoena the ISP.

11:21.793 --> 11:24.000
Alright, approach.

11:25.827 --> 11:27.482
This is off the record.

11:32.448 --> 11:33.931
