11:34.068 --> 11:36.758
to investigate my out of court
opinions is one thing,

11:36.896 --> 11:39.862
but that you would seek
to undermine and embarrass me,

11:40.000 --> 11:41.310
- is another.
- Your Honor...

11:41.448 --> 11:44.310
Miss Campbell,
I would think long and hard

11:44.448 --> 11:46.448
before asking me
to recuse myself.

11:46.586 --> 11:49.758
Yeah, thought about it.
We still want you to step down.

11:50.517 --> 11:54.275
You want another judge?
Be my guest.

11:55.103 --> 11:59.551
But, as I tell my grandkids,
actions have their consequences.

12:00.241 --> 12:02.551
Back on the record.

12:02.689 --> 12:04.827
Defense motion is granted.

12:07.758 --> 12:10.000
