and photos of his injuries.

15:25.517 --> 15:27.965
What was Jason's condition
after the incident?

15:28.103 --> 15:31.758
You can see the red marks
and welts here,

15:32.379 --> 15:35.620
and of course, the broken arm.

15:36.068 --> 15:38.103
