15:38.241 --> 15:41.655
extremely humiliating
and traumatizing.

15:41.793 --> 15:44.034
- Aren't you going to object?
- No.

15:44.172 --> 15:46.206
It wasn't at all reasonable.

15:46.482 --> 15:49.551
Objection, speculation and move
to strike the last statement,

15:49.689 --> 15:51.931
improper opinion
and ultimate question.

15:52.068 --> 15:53.586
- Overruled.
- Your Honor!

15:53.724 --> 15:56.310
Overruled. Counselor.

15:56.896 --> 16:00.758
- Nothing further.
- We'll resume after lunch.

16:06.068 --> 16:10.137
- What's wrong?
- Honestly, I'm not sure.

16:12.586 --> 16:13.931
Why didn't you object

16:14.068 --> 16:15.482
to Montgomery's
testimony unreasonableness?

16:15.620 --> 16:17.310
