testimony more credibility.

16:21.620 --> 16:22.896
But he was rendering a legal--

16:23.034 --> 16:24.551
I don't have to agree
with you, Gwen.

16:24.689 --> 16:26.379
Why do you have
such a problem with that?

16:26.517 --> 16:28.931
- I don't, I--
- You seem to.

16:29.448 --> 16:31.241
Look, forget it, just...
it's done, okay?

16:31.379 --> 16:33.000
What we got to do now
is we need to show

16:33.137 --> 16:35.137
that Donielle is a good mother
and not a monster

16:35.275 --> 16:36.896
and we need to emphasize
the part of the statute

16:37.034 --> 16:39.172
that says corporal punishment
is okay if you reasonably

16:39.310 --> 16:41.413
believe it's necessary
to maintain discipline.

16:41.551 --> 16:43.448
And so, the more misbehaving
your child is,

16:43.586 --> 16:46.586
the more reasonable
